---
import BaseHead from "../components/BaseHead.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from "../consts";
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<h1>üßë‚Äçüéì SammySam Academy!</h1>
			<p>
				Welcome to the official <a href="https://www.openenglish.com"
					>English Academy</a
				> website. This site is the perfect starting point for anyone looking to
				improve their English skills, whether you're a beginner or looking to refine
				your fluency.
			</p>
			<p>
				This platform comes with a variety of courses and resources to help you
				achieve your language goals. You can personalize your learning
				experience by choosing courses that suit your needs, from grammar to
				conversation practice.
			</p>
			<p>Here are a few ideas on how to get started with the academy:</p>
			<ul>
				<li>
					Sign up for our free trial in <code>src/pages/signup.astro</code>
				</li>
				<li>
					Browse available courses in <code>src/pages/courses.astro</code>
				</li>
				<li>
					Learn more about our instructors in <code
						>src/components/Instructor.astro</code
					>
				</li>
				<li>
					Check out our blog for English tips and learning resources in <code
						>src/content/blog/</code
					>
				</li>
				<li>
					Join a live conversation class to practice your speaking skills in <code
						>src/pages/classes.astro</code
					>
				</li>
			</ul>
			<p>
				We hope you enjoy your learning journey! If you have any questions,
				remember to <a href="https://www.englishacademy.com/docs"
					>read our guide</a
				> or <a href="https://www.englishacademy.com/chat">join us on chat</a> to
				ask for assistance.
			</p>
			<p>
				Looking for more resources to help with your studies? Check out our
				partner <a href="https://www.languagelearning.com"
					>Language Learning Hub</a
				>.
			</p>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
